'''摩梭语'''是[[纳语组|纳语组]][[纳西语组|纳西语组]]一种语言。

==方言==
'''永宁土话'''分布在丽江市永宁镇，由向柏霖 and Michaud (2011)记录。<ref>Jacques, Guillaume, and Alexis Michaud. 2011. "[http://www.benjamins.nl/series/dia/28-4/02jac.additional.pdf Approaching the historical phonology of three highly eroded Sino-Tibetan languages]." ''Diachronica'' 28.</ref>{{rp|468-498}}

'''拉达地土话'''只有2个声调。<ref>Dobbs, Roselle, and La Mingqing. 2016 "The two-level tonal system of Lataddi Narua." ''Linguistics of the Tibeto-Burman Area'', Vol. 39:1 (2016). {{doi|10.1075/ltba.39.1.04dob}}</ref>{{rp|67–104}}

